ou want to set up":[""],"Search for a company...":[""],"Settings saved successfully":[""],"Enter API credentials to connect with the company":[""],"Credentials verified and saved":[""],"Where can I find API credentials?":[""],"Contact Maystro team to get API credentials":[""],"Check the company dashboard or contact support":[""],"Rates imported successfully":[""],"An error occurred while importing":[""],"This may take 1-2 minutes depending on the provider":[""],"Please do not close this page":[""],"Import shipping rates and zones from":[""],"Import completed successfully":[""],"Completed in":[""],"Home Delivery":[""],"Office Pickup":[""],"Home Delivery Label":[""],"Example: Home Delivery":[""],"Office Pickup Label":[""],"Example: Office Pickup":[""],"Import may take 1-2 minutes depending on the number of zones":[""],"Skip":[""],"Setup Complete!":[""],"Your store is now ready to receive orders and create shipping labels":[""],"Go to Dashboard":[""],"Start":[""],"License":[""],"Provider":[""],"Complete":[""],"Do you want to skip setup? You can complete it later.":[""],"Are you sure you want to delete all the custom status ? this cannot be undone!":[""],"Are you sure you want to delete this order status ? this cannot be undone !":[""],"Status Name":[""],"characters max allowed":[""],"Status slug":[""],"Status Color":[""],"Status background":[""],"Add to bulk action":[""],"Preview":[""],"Order Status Manager":[""],"Customize the order status as your need":[""],"Add new status":[""],"Reset status":[""],"Update":[""],"Add New Status":[""],"Are you sure you want to clear cache?":[""],"Cache has been cleared":[""],"Are you sure you want to clear shipping zones?":[""],"Shipping Zones has been cleared":[""],"Order Settings":[""],"Configure default order behavior":[""],"Default Order Status":[""],"Select default status":[""],"Default status for new orders received from checkout":[""],"Automation":[""],"Automatic order processing and updates":[""],"Enable Auto Update":[""],"Automatically fetch tracking updates from shipping providers in the background":[""],"Update Interval (minutes)":[""],"Time between background updates (minimum 5 minutes)":[""],"Auto Update Orders":[""],"Automatically update order statuses when the scheduler runs":[""],"Auto Insert Orders":[""],"Automatically send orders to shipping provider when status changes":[""],"Trigger Status":[""],"Select status":[""],"Orders will be sent to shipping provider when changed to this status":[""],"Auto Mark as Dispatched":[""],"Automatically mark orders as dispatched in shipping provider":[""],"Dispatch Trigger Status":[""],"Checkout":[""],"Customize checkout page behavior":[""],"Extra Checkout Information":[""],"Display additional shipping info like desk address, phone, and location":[""],"New":[""],"Disable Custom Cities":[""],"Use default WooCommerce city field instead of custom city selector":[""],"Always Show Address":[""],"Always display the address field in checkout form":[""],"Features":[""],"Enable additional plugin features":[""],"Custom Order Status":[""],"Enable custom statuses like \"Delivery Attempted\" for better tracking":[""],"Green List (User Rating)":[""],"Check customer rating to identify potential spam orders (may slow down order page)":[""],"Custom Actions":[""],"Enable manual tracking and payment status controls":[""],"Advanced":[""],"Advanced configuration options":[""],"Product String Format":[""],"Default Shipping Note":[""],"e.g., Customer authorized to open package":[""],"This note will be added to all shipping labels":[""],"Debug Mode":[""],"Enable detailed logging for troubleshooting":[""],"Danger Zone":[""],"Irreversible and destructive actions":[""],"Clear Cache":[""],"Remove all cached data including cities, shipping rates, and provider responses. You may need to reconfigure some settings.":[""],"Clear Shipping Zones":[""],"Delete all shipping zones and methods. This will remove ALL shipping zones from WooCommerce.":[""],"Clear Zones":[""],"Save Settings":[""],"Close panel":[""],"Loading...":[""],"No tracking informations has been found":[""],"Ajouter Tracking Number":[""],"Please select a provider":[""],"Please enter a tracking number":[""],"An error occurred":[""],"Modifier Tracking Number":[""],"Select a provider":[""],"Saving":[""],"Getting Started":[""],"Introduction to Bordereau Generator":[""],"Learn what Bordereau Generator is and how it can help automate your shipping workflow.":[""],"Installation & Activation":[""],"Step-by-step guide to install and activate your license.":[""],"Dashboard Overview":[""],"Tour of the main dashboard and navigation.":[""],"Shipping Providers":[""],"Adding a Shipping Provider":[""],"How to connect your first shipping company.":[""],"Getting API Credentials":[""],"Where to find API tokens for Yalidine, ZR Express, Maystro, and others.":[""],"Import cities, prices, and pickup points from providers.":[""],"Setting Up Webhooks":[""],"Enable real-time tracking updates with webhooks.":[""],"Managing Orders":[""],"Creating Shipping Labels":[""],"Generate bordereau for your orders step by step.":[""],"Bulk Label Printing":[""],"Print multiple shipping labels at once.":[""],"Order Tracking":[""],"Monitor package status and delivery updates.":[""],"Settings & Automation":[""],"Auto Update Configuration":[""],"Set up automatic tracking status updates.":[""],"Automatic Order Insertion":[""],"Automatically send orders to shipping providers.":[""],"Checkout Customization":[""],"Customize the checkout experience for customers.":[""],"Advanced Features":[""],"Custom Order Statuses":[""],"Create and manage custom order statuses.":[""],"Troubleshooting Common Issues":[""],"Solutions for common problems and errors.":[""],"What is Bordereau Generator?":[""],"Bordereau Generator is a WooCommerce plugin that connects your store with 100+ Algerian shipping companies. It allows you to create shipping labels, track packages, and automate your delivery workflow.":[""],"How do I install the plugin?":[""],"1. Upload the plugin files to \/wp-content\/plugins\/\n2. Activate the plugin through the Plugins menu in WordPress\n3. Navigate to Bordereau Generator in your admin menu\n4. Go to Settings > License to enter your license key":[""],"What are the system requirements?":[""],"WordPress 5.0+, WooCommerce 4.0+, PHP 7.4+, and an active internet connection for API communication.":[""],"Is this plugin free?":[""],"No, Bordereau Generator is a paid plugin. Visit amineware.me to purchase a license or contact us via WhatsApp at +213783018210. If you obtained this plugin from another source, you have stolen 3 years of work and are not eligible for any support.":[""],"How do I activate my license key?":[""],"Go to Bordereau Generator > Settings > License tab, enter the license key you received after purchase, and click Activate.":[""],"Which shipping companies are supported?":[""],"We support 100+ providers including Yalidine, ZR Express, Maystro Delivery, Yalitec, Guepex, SpeedMail, EcoTrack, Noest, and many more.":[""],"How do I add a new shipping provider?":[""],"1. Go to the Shipping Providers tab\n2. Click on the provider card you want to enable\n3. Enter your API credentials\n4. Toggle the provider ON\n5. Click Save Settings":[""],"Where do I get API credentials?":[""],"Login to your shipping provider dashboard:\n\u2022 Yalidine: D\u00e9veloppement > Tableau de bord\n\u2022 ZR Express: API Rest > Jetons API\n\u2022 Maystro: Contact their team directly\n\u2022 Others: Check their dashboard or contact support":[""],"Can I use multiple providers at once?":[""],"Yes! You can enable and configure multiple shipping providers simultaneously. Customers can choose their preferred provider at checkout based on their location.":[""],"What does the Import button do?":[""],"The Import button fetches shipping rates, cities, and pickup points from the provider and creates WooCommerce shipping zones automatically. This saves you from manually configuring each zone.":[""],"Orders & Labels":[""],"How do I create a shipping label?":[""],"1. Go to WooCommerce > Orders\n2. Open the order you want to ship\n3. Find the Bordereau Generator metabox\n4. Select your shipping provider\n5. Verify customer details\n6. Click Create Bordereau":[""],"How does tracking work?":[""],"There are 3 ways to get tracking updates:\n1. Auto Update: Enable in Settings for periodic background updates\n2. Webhooks: Configure for real-time updates from the provider\n3. Manual: Click the Refresh button on the order page":[""],"What is COD (Cash on Delivery)?":[""],"COD means the customer pays upon delivery. The shipping company collects the payment and transfers it to you (minus their commission). This is the most common payment method in Algeria.":[""],"Can I print multiple labels at once?":[""],"Yes! Use the bulk actions feature in WooCommerce Orders. Select multiple orders, choose \"Print Bordereaux\" from the bulk actions dropdown, and click Apply.":[""],"Order Tracking Shortcodes":[""],"How do I create a tracking page for customers?":[""],"Create a new page in WordPress and add one of our tracking shortcodes. You can then add this page to your menu so customers can easily track their orders.":[""],"What is the [bordreau_tracking] shortcode?":[""],"This shortcode creates a tracking form where customers enter their Order ID and Phone Number to track their order. Add it to any page:\n\n[bordreau_tracking]\n\nCustomers will need their order number (e.g., #1234) and the billing phone number.":[""],"What is the [bordreau_tracking_by_tracking_number] shortcode?":[""],"This shortcode creates a simpler tracking form where customers only need the shipping tracking number:\n\n[bordreau_tracking_by_tracking_number]\n\nThis is useful when you send customers the tracking number directly.":[""],"Can I customize the shortcode tag?":[""],"Yes! Use WordPress filters to change the shortcode tag:\n\nadd_filter('bordreau_tracking_shortcode_tag', function() {\n    return 'my_custom_tracking';\n});":[""],"What is Auto Update and should I enable it?":[""],"Auto Update automatically fetches tracking status updates from shipping providers in the background. Enable it if you want order statuses to update without manual intervention. Set the interval based on your order volume.":[""],"What does Auto Insert Orders do?":[""],"When enabled, orders are automatically sent to the shipping provider when they reach a specific status (e.g., Processing). This eliminates the need to manually create bordereaux for each order.":[""],"How do I customize the product string format?":[""],"Go to Settings > Advanced and modify the Product String Format. Available placeholders:\n\u2022 {title} - Product name\n\u2022 {qty} - Quantity\n\u2022 {sku} - SKU code\n\u2022 {attributes} - Product variations\n\u2022 {id} - Product ID":[""],"What happens when I clear the cache?":[""],"Clearing cache removes stored cities, shipping rates, and provider responses. This is useful when:\n\u2022 Provider updates their rates\n\u2022 You see outdated information\n\u2022 Troubleshooting issues\n\nYou may need to re-import shipping rates after clearing.":[""],"Technical Questions":[""],"Does it work with HPOS?":[""],"Yes, the plugin is fully compatible with WooCommerce High-Performance Order Storage (HPOS). No additional configuration is needed.":[""],"Can I customize the label format?":[""],"Yes, the plugin provides filters and hooks for developers to customize label generation and formatting. Check our developer documentation for available hooks.":[""],"Is there a REST API?":[""],"Yes! The plugin provides REST API endpoints:\n\u2022 POST \/wp-json\/bordereau\/v1\/create-label - Create shipping label\n\u2022 GET \/wp-json\/bordereau\/v1\/tracking\/{number} - Get tracking status\n\nSee API Reference in documentation.":[""],"Troubleshooting":[""],"Orders are not being sent to the provider":[""],"Check these common causes:\n1. Verify API credentials are correct\n2. Ensure the provider is enabled (toggled ON)\n3. Check your internet connection\n4. Enable Debug Mode in Settings > Advanced for detailed error logs\n5. Check WordPress error logs":[""],"Shipping rates not showing at checkout":[""],"Try these solutions:\n1. Click Import to fetch\/refresh rates\n2. Clear cache and re-import\n3. Verify shipping zones in WooCommerce > Settings > Shipping\n4. Check if the customer location is covered by your zones\n5. Ensure the provider is enabled":[""],"Tracking status is not updating":[""],"Check these:\n1. Verify webhook URL is configured correctly in provider dashboard\n2. Check if Auto Update is enabled in Settings\n3. Try manually triggering a status update from the order page\n4. Check if the tracking number is valid":[""],"How do I contact support?":[""],"Email us at support@amineware.me or visit amineware.me for documentation and help. Include your WordPress version, WooCommerce version, and any error messages.":[""],"Free":[""],"completed":[""],"Learning Center":[""],"Master Bordereau Generator with video tutorials and guides":[""],"Video Tutorials":[""],"Videos":[""],"Your Progress":[""],"lessons completed":[""],"Completed":[""],"Mark Complete":[""],"Free Lesson":[""],"Previous":[""],"Search FAQ...":[""],"Can't find what you're looking for?":[""],"Our support team is here to help you.":[""],"Webhook URL has been copied":[""],"Failed to copy URL":[""],"Webhook has been configured successfully":[""],"Failed to configure webhook":[""],"Webhook URL":[""],"This URL will be automatically registered with ZR Express 2.0":[""],"Copy this URL and paste it in your provider's webhook settings":[""],"Copied!":[""],"Copy":[""],"How to use":["\u0643\u064a\u0641\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0633\u062a\u062e\u062f\u0627\u0645"],"Copy the webhook URL above":["\u0627\u0646\u0633\u062e \u0631\u0627\u0628\u0637 Webhook \u0623\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0647"],"Go to your provider's dashboard":["\u0627\u0630\u0647\u0628 \u0625\u0644\u0649 \u0644\u0648\u062d\u0629 \u062a\u062d\u0643\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0632\u0648\u062f"],"Find the webhook\/integration settings":["\u0627\u0628\u062d\u062b \u0639\u0646 \u0625\u0639\u062f\u0627\u062f\u0627\u062a Webhook\/\u0627\u0644\u0631\u0628\u0637"],"Paste the URL and save":["\u0627\u0644\u0635\u0642 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0627\u0628\u0637 \u0648\u0627\u062d\u0641\u0638"],"Security Settings":["\u0625\u0639\u062f\u0627\u062f\u0627\u062a \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0645\u0627\u0646"],"Optional security token for webhook verification":["\u0631\u0645\u0632 \u0623\u0645\u0627\u0646 \u0627\u062e\u062a\u064a\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0644\u0644\u062a\u062d\u0642\u0642 \u0645\u0646 Webhook"],"Secret Key":[""],"The signing secret will be saved automatically if returned by the API, or you can enter it manually from your ZR Express webhook settings":["\u0633\u064a\u062a\u0645 \u062d\u0641\u0638 \u0633\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0648\u0642\u064a\u0639 \u062a\u0644\u0642\u0627\u0626\u064a\u064b\u0627 \u0625\u0630\u0627 \u062a\u0645 \u0625\u0631\u062c\u0627\u0639\u0647 \u0628\u0648\u0627\u0633\u0637\u0629 API\u060c \u0623\u0648 \u064a\u0645\u0643\u0646\u0643 \u0625\u062f\u062e\u0627\u0644\u0647 \u064a\u062f\u0648\u064a\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u0646 \u0625\u0639\u062f\u0627\u062f\u0627\u062a Webhook \u0627\u0644\u062e\u0627\u0635\u0629 \u0628\u0640 ZR Express"],"Optional secret key for verifying webhook requests":["\u0645\u0641\u062a\u0627\u062d \u0633\u0631\u064a \u0627\u062e\u062a\u064a\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0644\u0644\u062a\u062d\u0642\u0642 \u0645\u0646 \u0637\u0644\u0628\u0627\u062a Webhook"],"Signing secret from ZR Express dashboard":["\u0633\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0648\u0642\u064a\u0639 \u0645\u0646 \u0644\u0648\u062d\u0629 \u062a\u062d\u0643\u0645 ZR Express"],"Enter secret key (optional)":["\u0623\u062f\u062e\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0641\u062a\u0627\u062d \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0631\u064a (\u0627\u062e\u062a\u064a\u0627\u0631\u064a)"],"Save Webhook":[""],"Configure Webhook":[""],"Set up automatic order status updates":[""],"Configur